<section class="card">
  <h2>Message to the world</h2>

  <p>
    We believe freedom belongs to everyone — without exception.
    A free society is built on dignity, equality, and the right of every person
    to live without fear.
  </p>

  <div class="note">
    <strong>Peace • Respect • Equality</strong><br>
    We stand for peace, compassion, and the rejection of violence.
    We support equal rights for all people, regardless of nationality,
    gender, religion, language, or background.
  </div>

  <p>
    This archive exists to preserve public evidence and documentation.
    The goal is clarity, accountability, and a future shaped by justice and
    human dignity.
  </p>
